OL,3,CThreatening email 'hoax' which closed
OL,4,Cschools investigated
OL,6,FThe PSNI is working with the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police to investigate a
OL,8,Fpossible link between threatening
OL,9,Femails sent to schools in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, and similar incidents in
OL,11,FLondon earlier this month.
OL,13,FNine schools were targeted in
OL,14,FStrabane, Enniskillen and Ballycastle,
OL,15,Fwith six forced to close on Monday.
OL,17,FWhile the threats have been declared a
OL,18,Fhoax, it was a day of disruption for
OL,19,Fthousands of pupils, parents and
OL,20,Fteachers.
