OL,6,FPolice said officers were immediately
OL,7,Fdeployed to each school to engage with
OL,8,Fstaff.
OL,10,FA PSNI statement said: "Checks have
OL,11,Fnot, at this time, resulted in
OL,12,Fanything untoward at any of the
OL,13,Fschools. Based on enquiries and
OL,14,Finformation to date, police are
OL,15,Ftreating this as a hoax. Enquiries are
OL,16,Fcontinuing.
OL,18,F"Three schools in Enniskillen who
OL,19,Freceived the email stayed open while
OL,20,Fthe schools in Ballycastle and three
OL,21,Fin Strabane closed."
