OL,6,FChief Superintendent Gillian Kearney
OL,7,Fadded: "We take incidents of this
OL,8,Fnature very seriously and we
OL,9,Funderstand the concern in the
OL,10,Fcommunity, not to mention the
OL,11,Fdisruption it has caused in each of
OL,12,Fthe school communities and for
OL,13,Fstudents and parents.
OL,15,F"Thank you to each of the schools for
OL,16,Ftheir assistance with our enquiries to
OL,17,Fdate.
