OL,6,FIn a statement, the Education
OL,7,FAuthority said: "We have been working
OL,8,Fclosely with PSNI who have confirmed
OL,9,Fthat the threatening email sent to
OL,10,Fnine schools in Northern Ireland today
OL,11,Fis being treated as a hoax.
OL,13,F"PSNI immediately attended each school
OL,14,Fto engage with staff, and checks have
OL,15,Fnot resulted in anything untoward
OL,16,Fbeing identified at any of the
OL,17,Fschools. Police enquiries are
OL,18,Fcontinuing, and they will continue to
OL,19,Fliaise with each of the impacted
OL,20,Fschools. We are very grateful to PSNI
OL,21,Ffor their rapid response to this issue.
